{"tid":868754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那「殲-10S」墜機　疑駕駛員屍塊散落一地","createTime":"2018-10-19T17:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T01:07:35.000Z","uid":32511,"like":90,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"166731610aad99f5c466bf277f45d1648476acc3","tid":868754,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:52:08.000Z","msg":"傳中國空軍「殲-10S」戰機在廣東湛江墜毀，造成2人死亡。<br />\n <br />\n據《多維新聞網》報導，中國航空攝影師「DS大彪」，在微博指出，10月18日，中國一輛戰機墜毀，該戰機疑似為「殲-10S」雙座型戰機。隨後，網路上開始流傳墜機當地的照片影片，畫面中也有拍到解放軍八一軍徽的軍機殘骸，其中的一塊殘骸旁甚至有疑似屍塊的物體。<br />\n <br />\n據悉，軍機墜毀地點是中國空軍在廣東湛江的遂溪基地，主要負責中國南向地區的防務。而在過去數年中，殲-10系列戰機，包括殲-10A、殲-10B、殲-10S等都有墜毀的記錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/015125_02425cc3323b23fe7e58830c0d55fbce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F015125_02425cc3323b23fe7e58830c0d55fbce.png&h=32a3ea42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/20/015205_de26b4d680a9fe59d34928e97fba4918.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2F015205_de26b4d680a9fe59d34928e97fba4918.png&h=fce27d85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20ccf6bcb4616f1f483d3dc01bc9b4c2de02233e","tid":868754,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:54:08.000Z","msg":"彈性彈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cb2eb7ebf2d9f6bc4d4f26e4a3746ee24af498","tid":868754,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ef5190869793db69631b7ea449437dc535251d","tid":868754,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c